  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/abb326b42d5acae2e0ced492ee691139.avif?t=1667828695\" width=616 height=209 /></span><br><strong>Box Kid Adventures</strong> is a dynamic, top-down puzzle game.<br>You play as Box Kid – a toy made of cardboard – going through various levels, full of nasty enemies and brain challenging puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/63347d1d64a752a2782ab6c401b34f80.webp?t=1667828695\" width=615 height=29 /></span><br><i>\"In the age of electronics, the toy-robots became kids favourite playthings. However, a young, ambitious designer, created a new toy. A Kid. A Box Kid! A toy made out of cardboard. A toy that should breathe life into the world of imagination. But the company's CEO wasn't impressed by that idea and he threw Box Kid into the garbage chute... But was that the real reason? Unveil the truth, as you help Box Kid discover his destiny!\"</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/a1babc14c9a492ebb2d49c16cc3b78a3.webp?t=1667828695\" width=615 height=29 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...simple but deep gameplay, that really captures the spirit of the 8-bit era.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENJOY...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/94b274d942ac21d0f76ca2d9284d871b.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/94b274d942ac21d0f76ca2d9284d871b.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/94b274d942ac21d0f76ca2d9284d871b.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...beautiful, cartoon graphics in Hi-Definition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GO TROUGH...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/e85e508374c9425f2e6c2544d2c7745b.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/e85e508374c9425f2e6c2544d2c7745b.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/e85e508374c9425f2e6c2544d2c7745b.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...75 various levels, full of nasty enemies and brain challenging puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CREATE AND SHARE...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/b6398d4844c0421f4840fe370aa32167.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/b6398d4844c0421f4840fe370aa32167.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/b6398d4844c0421f4840fe370aa32167.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...your own levels, with the built-in level editor.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARN KEYS...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/f6729a5dae7d328526b4528624b5ad96.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/f6729a5dae7d328526b4528624b5ad96.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/f6729a5dae7d328526b4528624b5ad96.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...to unlock new characters and levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCOVER...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/10426cb6a5f03d81990a09a06f51bc0f.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/10426cb6a5f03d81990a09a06f51bc0f.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/10426cb6a5f03d81990a09a06f51bc0f.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>...the destiny of a cute cardboard hero.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/abb326b42d5acae2e0ced492ee691139.avif?t=1667828695\" width=616 height=209 /></span><br><strong>Box Kid Adventures</strong> is a dynamic, top-down puzzle game.<br>You play as Box Kid – a toy made of cardboard – going through various levels, full of nasty enemies and brain challenging puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/63347d1d64a752a2782ab6c401b34f80.webp?t=1667828695\" width=615 height=29 /></span><br><i>\"In the age of electronics, the toy-robots became kids favourite playthings. However, a young, ambitious designer, created a new toy. A Kid. A Box Kid! A toy made out of cardboard. A toy that should breathe life into the world of imagination. But the company's CEO wasn't impressed by that idea and he threw Box Kid into the garbage chute... But was that the real reason? Unveil the truth, as you help Box Kid discover his destiny!\"</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/a1babc14c9a492ebb2d49c16cc3b78a3.webp?t=1667828695\" width=615 height=29 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE...</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.poster.avif?t=1667828695\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.webm?t=1667828695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217870/extras/05bc724bd96dac9afc266400a9f4685d.mp4?t=1667828695\" type=